Message: Even though pleasure won't last forever, as long as Commandant is here, we'll surely have much more pleasure again!
It was so fun hanging around with Commandant, but I felt there weren't enough kinds of drinks. Next time, we'll handle the drinks for you. Speech input ended. Oh, Is it this button?
Commandant, after the event ends, please don't push yourself too hard and take rest days whenever you need to... Well then, I'll go to look for other members.
On behalf of the Engineering Force, we hope to see you again at the next event. I'm only speaking on behalf of the Engineering Force, okay?
It was getting noisier when people gathered around. Let's go somewhere quieter next time, just the two of us.
I'd have brought my harmonica if I'd known there would be so many events around. I'm looking forward to giving everyone my best performance next time.
With the sea waves softly rolling in and birds soaring in the sky, it couldn't be any better to create art with you.
We must hold an event like this one more time, Commandant! Let's meet up next week. I can't wait to see your event proposal! This is what Nanami wanted to tell you.
I've been told that I should wear something more appropriate for an event like this. What are your thoughts, Commandant? Or can you help me select my clothes?
It's good to have a place where you can soak your body in sea water. Thank you for bringing me here, Commandant.
Were you able to dig up this message, Commandant? This was pretty like how we dug you out of the sand. Perhaps we should just throw it into the sea next time.
A very entertaining event indeed. If that's possible, I'd love to have it in Kowloong as well. Would you help me out if that happens?
Did you enjoy the show, Commandant? It really feels good to forget everything and enjoy the sea from time to time, doesn't it?
When our squad was having a beach volleyball game, Lillian accidentally slammed the ball into Captain Palma's face. The anger in her eyes was...

SingleMessage[1]: It's been another year already. With you alongside us, the Gray Ravens will keep on striving toward a new future.
SingleMessage[2]: Another year that we've spent together has passed. I hope I can leave an anniversary message to you in each of the following years, Commandant.
SingleMessage[3]: It's good to see the Gray Raven, even after moving on to another new logbook, is still whole with everyone sticking together.

SingleMessage[1]: It has been a year brimming with cherished memories, Commandant. Let's continue this journey together in the times that lie ahead.
SingleMessage[2]: I've just unlocked a trophy for spending a year with you, Commandant. Can't wait to earn even more trophies in the new year!
SingleMessage[3]: It was a truly hectic year, wasn't it? Don't push yourself too hard, y'know. Watch over your sleep time, quality, hideout...
SingleMessage[4]: No matter how many years have passed, there's only one thing I can do for you and themâ€”destroy everything that gets in the way.

SingleMessage[1]: A year has passed, which means I've already observed you for a whole year... That said, time itself has no meaning to me.
SingleMessage[2]: The only thing that matters is not how long we've been together, but what we want to achieve together. Hope you can find it to sustain our relationship.
SingleMessage[3]: A year's plays have ended. I wonder what plays are in store for the new year. How about you, Commandant? Want some... surprise?

RewardName: Arrival Target / Fate Arrival Target Character
SingleMessage[1]: This is specifically for you, so you gotta come over and say your thank you in person, got it?
To commemorate our anniversary, I've drawn a portrait of you. What do you say we take a look at it together in my art studio?
SingleMessage[2]: Even though I'm not here with you, I wish the wind of fortune will blow behind your sails, Commandant.

SingleMessage[1]: Congratulations on getting my anniversary message, Commandant! Collect six more and you'll be able to summon Nanami!
SingleMessage[2]: In return for your companionship over the past year, I shall accompany you through the new year. A reasonable exchange indeed.

SingleMessage[1]: I must say over the past year, you often pushed yourself too much, Commandant. Please remember I'm here for you whenever things stress you out.

RewardName: Arrival Target / Fate Arrival Target Character
SingleMessage[1]: Two questions: Any idea how many messes I cleaned up for you over the past year? How're you gonna repay me in the new year?
SingleMessage[2]: Commandant, let's celebrate the anniversary with some card games. You, me, and Buddy... Perfect.

SingleMessage[1]: A year has gone by, yet my spear will remain at your service, ready to wipe out any obstacles in your path, Commandant.
As time flies by, everything changes. Though I often find this pleasurable, something should just stay as is. Don't you think so, Commandant?
SingleMessage[2]: Wow, it's already been another year?! I was barely even aware of it! Let's make an anniversary cake together, Commandant!

SingleMessage[1]: I hope this will bring blessings upon you, Commandant. May you be safe and happy in the new year.
Bambinata from the past would want you to have this. Thank you for your caring and kindness, Commandant.
Another year passed. You know you're welcome to drop by anytime you want. I've just got a new guitar. I want you to listen to a song I created recently.

RewardName: Arrival Target / Fate Arrival Target Character
SingleMessage[1]: I'm looking forward to continuing the pursuit of the goals left undone from last year with you, Commandant.
SingleMessage[2]: Into the new year we go! Let me know anytime you need backup. All the bills've been sent to Nikola's office, don't worry!
